{"type":"message","id":"9578c6b2","parentId":"c8293e2b","timestamp":"2026-02-20T01:21:44.130Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_2boxjvy09t2h_1","toolName":"cron","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"jobs\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"31240d42-43aa-4b12-8a55-cdada12782a9\",\n      \"agentId\": \"main\",\n      \"name\": \"A股每日资讯\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1771426816719,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1771550400026,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"expr\": \"10 9 * * *\",\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"tz\": \"Asia/Shanghai\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"请抓取最新的A股资讯（人工智能、机器人、热门板块相关），整理成【HTML简报格式】发送到邮箱 qn_home@163.com，标题格式为：A股开盘前资讯 - 今日日期。\\n\\n【重要要求】\\n1. 必须从【至少4个不同来源】抓取资讯：第一财经、东方财富、新浪财经、同花顺、财联社、每日经济新闻等\\n2. 【不要放链接】- 将资讯要点直接总结展示在邮件正文中，每条资讯需要包含【标题+100字左右的内容摘要】\\n3. 使用 /root/.openclaw/workspace/a-stock-news-v4.html 作为样式模板\\n4. 每个板块至少精选【TOP 20条】重要资讯\\n5. 确保包含：标题、日期、机器人/AI板块、美股市场、机构观点、科创板、宏观数据等板块\\n6. 【邮件发送】：必须以MIME text/html 格式发送邮件，确保邮件显示为渲染后的HTML页面\"\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"announce\",\n        \"channel\": \"email\",\n        \"to\": \"qn_home@163.com\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1771636200000,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1771549800007,\n        \"lastStatus\": \"error\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 600019,\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 2,\n        \"lastError\": \"Error: cron: job execution timed out\"\n      }\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"details":{"jobs":[{"id":"31240d42-43aa-4b12-8a55-cdada12782a9","agentId":"main","name":"A股每日资讯","enabled":true,"createdAtMs":1771426816719,"updatedAtMs":1771550400026,"schedule":{"expr":"10 9 * * *","kind":"cron","tz":"Asia/Shanghai"},"sessionTarget":"isolated","wakeMode":"now","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"请抓取最新的A股资讯（人工智能、机器人、热门板块相关），整理成【HTML简报格式】发送到邮箱 qn_home@163.com，标题格式为：A股开盘前资讯 - 今日日