{"type":"message","id":"0724d904","parentId":"487ed3e1","timestamp":"2026-02-20T01:23:09.952Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Can't access that session history. Let me summarize what I know about the cron job issue for Boss.\n\nBased on the cron list and runs:\n1. The job \"A股每日资讯\" runs daily at 9:10 AM\n2. Last run status: error - \"cron: job execution timed out\" (600019ms = 10 minutes)\n3. It looks like the job is taking too long and timing out\n\nThe error \"Write failed: Missing required parameter: path\" might be a separate issue or could be related to the timeout causing incomplete execution.\n\nI should tell Boss what I found.","thinkingSignature":"729ee76b89323433ebd802f6f75e3d9a7404ad2b512c205b972eb80471d9a2dc"},{"type":"text","text":"根据 cron 记录，问题大概是酱紫的：\n\n**「A股每日资讯」任务**\n- 📅 每天 9:10 运行\n- ❌ 最近两次都失败了\n- ⚠️ **原因：执行超时**（超过 10 分钟被系统 kill 了）\n\n任务流程是：抓取 4+ 个来源的资讯 → 整理成 HTML → 发邮件。可能是因为抓取资讯太多、太耗时，导致超时。\n\n**解决方案：**\n1. **减少资讯量** — 目前要求 TOP 20 条，可以减少到 10 条\n2. **增加超时时间** — 目前 cron 默认 10 分钟超时\n3. **优化抓取逻辑** — 减少重复抓取\n\n要调整任务配置吗？比如把资讯数量改少一点？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":2707,"output":285,"cacheRead":13486,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":16478,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771550569748}}
