{"type":"message","id":"6afe88e2","parentId":"e2b6772f","timestamp":"2026-02-20T01:24:24.025Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to:\n1. Reduce the number of news items from 20 to 10\n2. Increase the timeout from 10 minutes to 30 minutes\n\nI need to update the cron job. The job ID is 31240d42-43aa-4b12-8a55-cdada12782a9.\n\nFor the timeout, I need to check the cron schema - it seems like there's a timeoutSeconds option in the payload for agentTurn. Let me update the job with:\n1. The message/payload updated to ask for 10 items instead of 20\n2. Add timeoutSeconds to the agentTurn payload (30 minutes = 1800 seconds)","thinkingSignature":"93517c1152b6b046c9c55eb73905e7b18ba0adaf3200c13eab139c90175105f7"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_54nfnffrh7fu_1","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"update","jobId":"31240d42-43aa-4b12-8a55-cdada12782a9","patch":{"payload":{"message":"请抓取最新的A股资讯（人工智能、机器人、热门板块相关），整理成【HTML简报格式】发送到邮箱 qn_home@163.com，标题格式为：A股开盘前资讯 - 今日日期。\n\n【重要要求】\n1. 必须从【至少4个不同来源】抓取资讯：第一财经、东方财富、新浪财经、同花顺、财联社、每日经济新闻等\n2. 【不要放链接】- 将资讯要点直接总结展示在邮件正文中，每条资讯需要包含【标题+100字左右的内容摘要】\n3. 使用 /root/.openclaw/workspace/a-stock-news-v4.html 作为样式模板\n4. 每个板块至少精选【TOP 10条】重要资讯\n5. 确保包含：标题、日期、机器人/AI板块、美股市场、机构观点、科创板、宏观数据等板块\n6. 【邮件发送】：必须以MIME text/html 格式发送邮件，确保邮件显示为渲染后的HTML页面","timeoutSeconds":1800}}}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":28,"output":433,"cacheRead":7823,"cacheWrite":8377,"totalTokens":16661,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771550653640}}
