arget <E.164|group JID>\\\",\\n      \\\"summary\\\": \\\"已完成A股每日资讯简报的抓取和发送！\\\\n\\\\n**发送详情：**\\\\n- 📧 收件人：nohotnnn@gmail.com\\\\n- 📝 标题：A股开盘前资讯 - 2026年2月19日\\\\n- ✅ 状态：发送成功\\\\n\\\\n**简报要点：**\\\\n1. **机器人/AI热点**：春晚引爆机器人热潮，宇树科技、松延动力、银河通用等企业亮相；腾讯元宝DAU超5000万；谷歌Gemini上线音乐模型\\\\n2. **美股市场**：三大指数收涨，纳指涨0.78%，存储概念股普涨\\\\n3. **机构观点**：李迅雷认为A股稳中向好，机会在科技领域\\\\n4. **科创板**：半导体、光通信领涨，禾信仪器涨近50%创历史新高\\\\n5. **宏观数据**：人民币全球支付占比3.13%\\\",\\n      \\\"runAtMs\\\": 1771463400003,\\n      \\\"durationMs\\\": 460183,\\n      \\\"nextRunAtMs\\\": 1771549800000,\\n      \\\"sessionId\\\": \\\"d64a584a-02ed-4006-93ff-799ff8143480\\\",\\n      \\\"sessionKey\\\": \\\"agent:main:cron:31240d42-43aa-4b12-8a55-cdada12782a9:run:d64a584a-02ed-4006-93ff-799ff8143480\\\"\\n    },\\n    {\\n      \\\"ts\\\": 1771550400036,\\n      \\\"jobId\\\": \\\"31240d42-43aa-4b12-8a55-cdada12782a9\\\",\\n      \\\"action\\\": \\\"finished\\\",\\n      \\\"status\\\": \\\"error\\\",\\n      \\\"error\\\": \\\"Error: cron: job execution timed out\\\",\\n      \\\"runAtMs\\\": 1771549800007,\\n      \\\"durationMs\\\": 600019,\\n      \\\"nextRunAtMs\\\": 1771636200000\\n    }\\n  ]\\n}\",\"_meta\":{\"runtime\":\"node\",\"runtimeVersion\":\"22.22.0\",\"hostname\":\"unknown\",\"name\":\"openclaw\",\"date\":\"2026-02-20T02:07:48.746Z\",\"logLevelId\":3,\"logLevelName\":\"INFO\",\"path\":{\"fullFilePath\":\"file:///usr/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/entry.js:2051:46\",\"fileName\":\"entry.js\",\"fileNameWithLine\":\"entry.js:2051\",\"fileColumn\":\"46\",\"fileLine\":\"2051\",\"filePath\":\"/usr/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/entry.js\",\"filePathWithLine\":\"/usr/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/entry.js:2051\",\"method\":\"console.log\"}},\"time\":\"2026-02-20T02:07:48.749Z\"}\n{\"0\":\"{\\\"subsystem\\\":\\\"agent/embedded\\\"}\",\"1\":\"embedded run tool end: runId=c48a5092-e4e5-44a5-a341-b08356bfc1fe tool=exec toolCallId=call_function_jrli3ipq6jqa_1\",\"_meta\":{\"runtime\":\"node\",\"runtimeVersion\":\"22.22.0\",\"