{"type":"message","id":"db04978e","parentId":"91545fe5","timestamp":"2026-02-20T10:27:49.827Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see the issue - there are old dates in the news. Most news is from Feb 18-19, with only 11 from Feb 20. This is because:\n1. The news sources might not have much new content for Feb 20 yet (it's still early morning)\n2. The agent isn't properly prioritizing the most recent news\n\nI need to update the cron task to be more explicit about requiring only news from the past 24 hours (Feb 19-20), and to prioritize the most recent news.","thinkingSignature":"2480df9c29161f6ac842f760fd76f8b954e33fa355170cdb26d1286fc540eefe"},{"type":"text","text":"确实有问题！资讯日期很乱：2月17日、18日、19日的都有，2月20日的只有11条。\n\n问题在于任务描述不够明确，让我改一下 cron 任务，强调要**最新24小时内的新闻**：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_6eobzlky0uj0_1","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"update","jobId":"31240d42-43aa-4b12-8a55-cdada12782a9","patch":{"payload":{"message":"请抓取最新的A股资讯（人工智能、机器人、热门板块相关），整理成【HTML简报格式】发送到邮箱 qn_home@163.com，标题格式为：A股开盘前资讯 - 今日日期。\n\n【重要要求】\n1. 【关键】只抓取过去24小时内的新闻（今天是2026年2月20日，所以只抓取2月19日和2月20日的资讯），不要抓取2月18日及更早的新闻！\n2. 必须从【至少4个不同来源】抓取资讯：第一财经、东方财富、新浪财经、同花顺、财联社、每日经济新闻等\n3. 【不要放链接】- 将资讯要点直接总结展示在邮件正文中，每条资讯需要包含【标题+100字左右的内容摘要】\n4. 使用 /root/.openclaw/workspace/a-stock-news-final.html 作为样式模板\n5. 每个板块至少精选【TOP 10条】重要资讯（必须是最新24小时内的）\n6. 确保包含：标题、日期、机器人/AI板块、美股市场、机构观点、科创板、宏观数据等板块\n7. 【邮件发送】：必须以MIME text/html 格式发送邮件，确保邮件显示为渲染后的HTML页面"}}}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":53488,"output":498,"cacheRead":13486,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":67472,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771583258849}}
